data.description: SELLER WILL CONTRIBUTE $15,000 TOWARDS BUYERS CLOSING COSTS with full price offer! Welcome to your dream home in the exclusive gated community of Johns Landing! This spacious 4-bedroom, 3-bathroom residence features an open floor plan, wood floors, and a chef's dream kitchen with Corian countertops and stainless steel appliances. The backyard is a peaceful and private oasis with a sound wall that blocks any highway noise. Home also features solar panels which has resulted in NO ELECTRIC BILL (an estimated savings of $150/month) for the current owner. Enjoy exclusive water access to Johns Lake for boating and fishing. Conveniently located near downtown Orlando and Winter Garden, this property offers a perfect balance of tranquility and city life.  Don't miss this incredible opportunity - schedule your private tour today!
